7
00:00:19.222 --> 00:00:24.290
In your first 30 days of being a manager,
what's different?

8
00:00:24.290 --> 00:00:29.280
Your perspectives is different, it's not
immediate, but it happens really slowly.

9
00:00:29.280 --> 00:00:33.255
