it's not usually that spicy or exciting.

31
00:01:48.434 --> 00:01:52.877
I was a little disappointed, honestly,
I thought this is gonna be like,

32
00:01:52.877 --> 00:01:57.410
I'm in the inner circle, but
it's really not that exciting, all right?

33
00:01:57.410 --> 00:02:03.430
A fun one was, you don't know how much
money everybody makes on your team.

34
00:02:03.430 --> 00:02:07.255
Doesn't really change anything,
you're like, interesting,

35
00:02:07.255 --> 00:02:10.870
but it's just an interesting
thing that you can look up now.

36
00:02:10.870 --> 00:02:14.347
Just a different perspective on how
much everybody is getting paid, and

37
00:02:14.347 --> 00:02:17.995
chances are it's gonna be different,
it's probably gonna surprise you.

38
00:02:17.995 --> 00:02:22.565
You don't have to do anything about it,
