39
00:02:22.565 --> 00:02:26.079
Another one is your calendar is all
meetings now, it starts off slowly,

40
00:02:26.079 --> 00:02:29.419
your manager's probably gonna add
a bunch of calendars, invites,

41
00:02:29.419 --> 00:02:33.180
your job now is to set up one-on-ones,
your job's to set up team meetings.

42
00:02:33.180 --> 00:02:34.852
Your job is to meet with partners and

43
00:02:34.852 --> 00:02:37.490
stakeholders, now the calendar
is slowly filling up.

44
00:02:38.490 --> 00:02:42.270
