00:04:10.339 --> 00:04:14.434
you need to know what's important and
what you can probably backburner.

69
00:04:14.434 --> 00:04:16.571
It's tricky, it's something you
have to adapt really quickly.

70
00:04:20.545 --> 00:04:25.940
At a team level, what's different is your
managers now one level up, generally.

71
00:04:25.940 --> 00:04:28.621
So that means the things they talk
about in the context of shares,

72
00:04:28.621 --> 00:04:29.610
it's very different.

73
00:04:30.610 --> 00:04:33.613
When you're just dealing
with your manager,

74
00:04:33.613 --> 00:04:38.702
they have a particular experience or
context they wanna share a perspective.

75
